// Win32 resource — gives Quest Home Editor.exe its file icon (shown in Explorer / taskbar).
1 ICON "app.ico"

// Google platform-tools adb (adb.exe + AdbWinApi.dll + AdbWinUsbApi.dll), zipped and EMBEDDED in the exe so a
// fully offline machine still gets adb: the editor extracts these beside itself if no external adb is found and
// there's no network to download. adb is redistributable (SideQuest/scrcpy bundle it too). See editor.h ensureAdb.
ADBWINZIP RCDATA "embed/adb-win.zip"
